# CMIP7 ScenarioMIP harmonisation+infilling inputs are version-controlled
# (chapter-owned choices: which history, which aneris overrides, which
# GHG-inversion series). The ScenarioMIP infilling DB is large (~3 MB) and
# fetched from Zenodo 20566343 -- see docs/data_setup.md.
!data/cmip7/
!data/cmip7/history_cmip7_scenariomip.csv
!data/cmip7/aneris-overrides-global.csv
!data/cmip7/cmip7_ghg_inversions.csv
data/cmip7/infilling_db_*.csv

